snippet.title: Froglike: The Frog Roguelike - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Froglike is a fast paced retro arcade adventure with roguelike elements.

Can you survive until the end of time itself? Download links below:

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Jimjum.Froglike
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/froglike-the-frog-roguelike/id1571357790

The Lily of Time is under attack by evil bugs, and with the last of his strength, Chronos (the frog version) reached out through spacetime to summon the prophecised saviour of time - and accidentally summoned a frog.

Now they’re stuck together, and this frog is the world’s only hope!

Playing as the Nameless Frog, players must complete two key objectives:

*Survive until the end of time itself by avoiding an onslaught of deadly enemies.
*Keep the Lily of Time powered up as long as possible to gain points and break high scores.

Secondary objectives include spinning aimlessly as time collapses around you, and trying not to fall into the water.

Time is kind of a big deal in this game.




--


OST Album: https://open.spotify.com/album/4jC1LwDQxgvQk3dzIKcBe0?si=NYsAB1w4RPmqfBUq_Hb_Xw&dl_branch=1
